      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOME HIGH (1) kicked off his career with an easy win as a hot favourite in Tasmania then performed well against some good opposition last start, coming from wider for third in the Rising Star at Ballarat. He looks well placed here and should get every chance from the ace draw. BAYSTYLE (11) finished 1.5m in front of SOME HIGH when runner-up in the Rising Star. Cops a tougher draw but he has yet to miss the top-two including a hat trick of wins, one of them at this venue. TALKBABYTALK (2) had a tough draw on the back row when midfield last time so is much better served by this barrier and was racing well prior with three wins and a second from the previous four outings. HUNGRY HOGARTH (6) has won here before and did a good job to miss narrowly in the latest outing at Charlton.",
